setInfo.name: EX Team Magma vs Team Aqua
setInfo.description: The fourth set in the EX Series, featuring the rivalry between Team Magma and Team Aqua from the Hoenn region. Introduces dual-type Pokémon cards and team-specific trainer cards. Features the legendary weather duo Kyogre and Groudon alongside their respective evil teams, plus the legendary beasts as Pokémon-ex cards.
